snippet.title: Dead Rising 4 - Official Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Watch the official launch trailer for Dead Rising 4. More weapons. More zombies. More fun than a shopping mall on Black Friday. ‘Tis the Season of the Unliving - Let the Slay Ride Begin!
